{"tid":1289881,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"英國邊個黨支持 BNO 變 BC，呢世都投佢！","createTime":"2019-07-06T09:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T05:25:45.000Z","uid":6034,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d28d2fbec972c66d857cffe51f10b9d7f8ebf259","tid":1289881,"uid":6034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T09:39:25.000Z","msg":"God save the Queen"},{"pid":"6cb8d099865be04bfbb514a9aa780efba2014d33","tid":1289881,"uid":108258,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T09:43:55.000Z","msg":"橫掂都係ff 最好得黑警冇得轉bc 最後真香港人走曬去英國做二等公民 得番啲黑警同腥港人留返喺香港 一國一制 享受中國人光榮"},{"pid":"18ee4f05b70726cf05dfea4412deae3f3a24d3ff","tid":1289881,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:56:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ddf2439f68437a7bfc09d1468c868e7db89891a","tid":1289881,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:57:30.000Z","msg":"但英國人會投?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb875275818be1af5644018e52462192664d32e","tid":1289881,"uid":188849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18ee4f05b70726cf05dfea4412deae3f3a24d3ff","tid":1289881,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:56:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T05:25:45.000Z","msg":"有方法知你父母有冇講大話：<br />\n30. 我不清楚我是否有過BN(O)身份，有方法查詢?<br />\n可以使用「身分證大法」得知你是否BN(O):<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">合符以下條件基本上可以肯定你有過BNO身份：\n- 1997年7月1日前未滿11歲\n- 身份證首次簽發日期為(06-97)或之前\n- 香港出世而且出世紙寫有'Established'</code></pre><br />\n全中以上三項條件代表你父母曾經在主權移交前代你申請過BNO<br />\n不符合以上全部條件並不代表你沒有過BNO身份<br />\n詳細身分證大法資訊請參閱Doc有關該大法部份<br />\n<br />\n中晒就入嚟啦<br />\n『薪火Post』BNO續期資訊(42) 繼續香港終局延長戰：記得登記做選民!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1263095\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1263095</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}